                  <div class="bg-green-900/30 p-2 rounded">
                    <div class="font-bold text-green-400">Phase 1</div>
                    <div class="text-white">Routine processes</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="bg-yellow-900/30 p-2 rounded">
                    <div class="font-bold text-yellow-400">Phase 2</div>
                    <div class="text-white">Complex workflows</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="bg-blue-900/30 p-2 rounded">
                    <div class="font-bold text-blue-400">Phase 3</div>
                    <div class="text-white">Strategic processes</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="border border-primary p-6 rounded-lg">
                <h4 class="font-bold text-primary mb-3">3. Monitor Performance & Continuously Optimize</h4>
                <p class="text-white">
                  Establish comprehensive monitoring for workflow performance, user satisfaction, and business outcomes. Use this data to identify optimization opportunities and adjust AI parameters for improved efficiency and accuracy.
                </p>
